question
Write a function isArrayInArg that takes two values value1 and value2 as arguments and returns true if at least one of the arguments
is an array, and false otherwise.
Example:
the isArrayInArg (12, [1]) function must return true;
the isArrayInArg ([], "Welcome") function must return true;
the isArrayInArg ([1], [0]) function must return true;
the isArrayInArg (15, 0) function must return false;
isArrayInArg ({name: 'Alice'}, "Bob") function should return false

solution:

function isArrayInArg(value1, value2){
  if(Array.isArray(value1) || Array.isArray(value2)) return true;
  else
  return false;
}
